title: Dajio Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located on Ocracoke Island in the village of Ocracoke. Has indoor seating, an outdoor patio surrounded with plants and festive lights, and an indoor bar area. Uses local ingredients. Showcases local artisans and local musicians. Also has a garden where they grow some of their ingredients. Most of the entrees are seafood based, but they do have vegan tacos clearly labeled on the menu, plus others that may be vegan or could be made vegan; please inquire.
